{
  "stem": "19969.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 92.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One peculiar thing also that happened, there was another-- the two officers in a jeep who were following General Linden were both West Point officers, Colonel [?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Bolduc, ?] who was the regimental commander, and Colonel Valens, who was a battalion commander.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, Valens testified at great length.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But Colonel [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Bolduc ?] was never called as a witness, either.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was there all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He became the chief of staff for the 42nd Division.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was never questioned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was one of the key witnesses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My guess is that Colonel [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Bolduc ?] wouldn't back up what the others have said.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I think he was an honorable man and would not back up the stories told by Valens and Lindon.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Lindon, in fact, says he never saw-- there was some shooting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But he never saw those German soldiers being killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The hell he didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was right there on the spot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And Valens was right there on the spot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And Valens said, m he shot at them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But his gun jammed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But in his previous story, he made a great mistake.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He wrote a long account of that right after that, in which he said he and his men charged this guard tower with blazing rifles and killed everybody in there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "That's on the record.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That's in the investigation also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But that-- when he came to testify on oath, he changed the story completely.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Said, well, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But his gun jammed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he said he was carrying a 45 submachine-- caliber submachine gun.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "What the hell a battalion commander is doing carrying a 45 subcaliber machine gun, I do not know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "That's not the normal-- normal armament for field-grade officers it is a 45 caliber pistol.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
